metadata.name: New Realms
metadata.description:
A recurring element in my photography: Man steps out of the dark into the light. Not only visually a very appealing theme but also as a story super exciting. Entering new realms, discovering new possibilities, full of courage, caution, and curiosity.
Starting a new phase, or even changing your life is represented by this simple visual that everyone can relate to.
